name: Innocent. Unattainable. Desirable.
description:
This is a similar work to René Gruau (4 February 1909 – 31 March 2004) a fashion illustrator. When I first seen this work - I thought of this woman ... She was Standing there .... Straight ... Accomplished .... My love ... feeling of coming closer ... may be touch ... the arch of her neck .... And the smell of her skin ... Warm skin on your lips ...

Hahaha - Fun =)
